flowchart TB
  subgraph before [Traditional optimistic oracle]
    M1[Market question]
    V1[Token vote / committee]
    C1[Contract trusts reported outcome]
    M1 --> V1 --> C1
  end

  subgraph after [ZK oracle aggregator]
    M2[Market question]
    S2[N independent sources]
    A2[Honest aggregation]
    P2[Groth16 proof]
    V2[Verifier]
    C2[Contract settles if proof valid]
    M2 --> S2 --> A2 --> P2 --> V2 --> C2
  end
